text: Respectfully, and with full disclosure you are not correct and will be proven wrong in your assertion. That's my last comment/tweet on this subject. I trust if/when proven wrong you will come back on this thread.
Irrelvant to what I have ascertained.
Divine: "Value is in the eye of the beholder."
Tom Brokaw is guilty of the allegation and the newscasters are guilty with regard to their reflexive and premature support of their fellow broadcaster @tombrokaw without having all the facts.
This will be my last comment or tweet on the Vester/Brokaw allegation.

I am a huge fan (and viewer) of @morningmika and @maddow - and will always be. I watch them religiously. I understand their reflexive reaction to support Brokaw - but Mika and Rachel are badly mistaken in granting support to him. deadline.com/2018/04/rachel-…

For a variety of reasons I believe the accusations by Linda Vester with regard to Tom Brokaw's sexual advances are 100% true. Our society is fortunate that there are brave women like Vester. money.cnn.com/2018/04/27/med… @maddow @AriMelber @morningmika @morning_joe @deborahkass
